  <refentry xml:id="function.chdir" xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
   <refnamediv>
    <refname>chdir</refname>
    <refpurpose>디렉토리를 변경합니다.</refpurpose>
   </refnamediv>
   <refsect1>
    <title>설명</title>
     <methodsynopsis>
      <type>bool</type><methodname>chdir</methodname>
      <methodparam><type>string</type><parameter>directory</parameter></methodparam>
     </methodsynopsis>
    <para>
     PHP의 현재 디렉토리를 <parameter>directory</parameter>로 변경합니다.
     &return.success;
    </para>
    <para>
     <example>
      <title><function>chdir</function> 예제</title>
       <programlisting role="php">
<![CDATA[
<?php
	
// 현재 디렉토리
echo getcwd() . "\n";
	
chdir('public_html');
	
// 현재 디렉토리
echo getcwd() . "\n";
	
?>
]]>
       </programlisting>
       <para>
        출력 예는:
       </para>
       <screen>
<![CDATA[
/home/vincent
/home/vincent/public_html
]]>
       </screen>
     </example>
    </para>
    &note.sm.uidcheck.dir;
    <para>
     참고: <function>getcwd</function>.
    </para>
   </refsect1>
  </refentry>

